file_content.text: Your efforts are for naught, Outlander.
You will never leave my station alive.
I do not see what you hope to accomplish.
You will go no further, Outlander.
You believe you have hurt the Eternal Empire. You are but a nuisance.
Welcome to my Star Fortress, Outlander. It will also serve nicely as your tomb.
I see. You think yourself a force to be reckoned with.
You are starting to get on my nerves.
Your journey has ended here before. So it will again!
Available units, converge on the Outlander.
I want the Outlander found. No excuses!
Let us be done with it already! Destroy the Outlander!
I am through with your nagging interruptions.
Death be upon you!
Do keep your guard up, Outlander.
I will destroy you!
Have a sample of our power.
As I thought. Back to more pressing matters....
You... die with me....
You have brought about your own doom!
Agh!
Your end is at hand....
The houses of Alderaan are mine to control!
You fool!
Stop at once!
Too stupid for words!
